(11,2,2,'Moodle updates are available (http://127.0.0.1:8080)','Update notifications\n\nThere is a newer Moodle version available!\nMoodle 5.0.6+ (Build: 20260327) Version 2025041406.09 (Stable version)\nMoodle 5.1.3+ (Build: 20260327) Version 2025100603.09 (Stable version)\nMoodle 4.5.10+ (Build: 20260327) Version 2024100710.06 (Stable version)\n\nSee http://127.0.0.1:8080/admin/index.php for more details\n\nIt is strongly recommended that you update your site to the latest version to obtain all recent security and bug fixes.\n\nYour Moodle site http://127.0.0.1:8080 is configured to automatically check for available updates. You are receiving this message as the administrator of the site. You can disable automatic checks for available updates in Site administration / Server / Update notifications or customise the delivery of this message via your preferences page.\n',2,'<h1>Update notifications</h1>\n<h2>There is a newer Moodle version available!</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Moodle 5.0.6+ (Build: 20260327)</strong> Version 2025041406.09 (Stable version)</li>\n<li><strong>Moodle 5.1.3+ (Build: 20260327)</strong> Version 2025100603.09 (Stable version)</li>\n<li><strong>Moodle 4.5.10+ (Build: 20260327)</strong> Version 2024100710.06 (Stable version)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See <a href=\"http://127.0.0.1:8080/admin/index.php\">http://127.0.0.1:8080/admin/index.php</a> for more details</p>\n<p>It is strongly recommended that you update your site to the latest version to obtain all recent security and bug fixes.</p>\n<footer><p style=\"font-size:smaller; color:#333;\">Your Moodle site <a href=\"http://127.0.0.1:8080\">http://127.0.0.1:8080</a> is configured to automatically check for available updates. You are receiving this message as the administrator of the site. You can disable automatic checks for available updates in Site administration / Server / Update notifications or customise the delivery of this message via your preferences page.</p></footer>','Update notifications','moodle','availableupdate',NULL,NULL,1774716279,1774714202,NULL),
